WEBVTT


00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.080
Having already banned overseas masters students

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:04.680
from bringing family members to the UK,

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:07.560
I have asked the Migration Advisory Committee

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:11.140
to review the Graduate Route to prevent abuse,

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:14.580
to protect the integrity and quality

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:19.620
of the UK's outstanding higher education sector.
